'''Anthony Wilford Brimley''' ([[September 27]], [[1930s|1934]] &ndash; [[August 1]], [[2020]]) portrayed the hermit [[Noa Briqualon]] in ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]'' ([[1985]]).

An early concept for [[Rio Durant]] from ''[[Solo: A Star Wars Story]]'' was based on Brimley.<ref>{{Twitter|PhilSzostak|status/1009179691071168512|[[Phil Szostak]]|quote=Famously-mustachioed actor Wilford Brimley (who also appeared as Noah Briqualon in 1985's Ewoks: The Battle for Endor) was an early influence on Rio Durant, then a gruff, mustachioed alien pilot with multiple eyes, as seen on p. 103 of The Art of #SoloAStarWarsStory|archivedate=20230423024051}}</ref>

